strings: <Cap><leader> discovers a new recipe for the alchemy pot!
<se_def>*: Curious travellers, if you value your lives, I urge you not to approach the ruins in the middle of the island.
<se_def>*: If you choose to ignore my advice, I cannot be held responsible for what happens to you.
<se_def>*: We chased that jester all the way here. But now that it's come to the crunch...
<se_def>*: I just can't see any hope of victory against someone strong enough to overpower Mr. Golding.
<se_def>*: But now we've come this far, we can hardly just turn around and go home... Oh! What to do, what to do...
<se_high>*: Why did that jester have to choose such a spooky hideout?
<se_high>*: If it wasn't so creepy here, we wouldn't hesitate to go after him!
